title: 'A Perfect Smartwatch'
body: Likes:  1. Good performance hardware 2. No lag till now as promised 3. Bluetooth hardware is latest so it doesn't disconnect itself from phone. Which is very important for a smart device. 4. Strap quality is good. 5. All available features working normal so not found any issue. 6. Battery is running as promised days (with Bluetooth connectivity and Active calling function). 7. Device Full charge in 2 hours which is good for 7-8 days battery life on moderate use.  Dislike:  1. Step counter is not accurate. 2. Sleep tracking is quite accurate. 3. Device doesn't have Screen Lock feature. It can be available on software updates.  This is the review after 15days usage. If I found any issue or update, I will post here. If anyone want to purchase this Fastrack New Limitless FS1 smartwatch should not think twice, Just Go for It.
